Locations.15:
For entry into the clubhouse, mask wearing will be optional to those individuals that have been vaccinated. Staff policing of this is not an option for us. Individuals will essentially be requested to be honor bound. We recognize the virus may still infect those vaccinated but the protection levels remain very high and we suggest masks and proper distancing as a way to minimize even more the chances of getting or spreading the disease.

For those choosing no vaccinations, masks must always be worn while inside the Clubhouse. We will not demand proof of negative testing results as this does not seem to guarantee an individual has not been exposed any time after the test.
